{"tid":1354241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說林鄭下臺，試着說中共滾出香港","createTime":"2019-07-23T06:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:27:59.000Z","uid":207710,"like":67,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5013887ff81e7d874cc706de79a1a20e88c47dfe","tid":1354241,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:01:27.000Z","msg":"根本香港政府只係一個傀儡<br />\n打倒林鄭只會有下一個林鄭<br />\n對準政權唔係要對準林鄭政府<br />\n而係要對準<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國共產黨</span></span><br />\n任何行動例如指責前線警察、黑社會、林鄭都只係爲咗削弱共產黨喺香港嘅管治威信<br />\n打呢啲目標嘅同時<br />\n點都要扯到<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國共產黨</span></span>喺背後嘅影響"},{"pid":"ca85daa5b25ddb8dc52e5bd970c841ebab08bb53","tid":1354241,"uid":207710,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:03:29.000Z","msg":"如果唔記得攻擊<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國共產黨</span></span><br />\n佢有咩事割晒其他人就可以全身而退"},{"pid":"54388b583aa81275c9ae9ef351a1e3fa74019b24","tid":1354241,"uid":207710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:05:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共產黨滾出香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"6cafdaac08b08cc6687ca090c28b881bb7d4c79c","tid":1354241,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"中國共產黨 躝返出香港"},{"pid":"e8fddcde703257c886ce86eafa1aee782c697663","tid":1354241,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:05:38.000Z","msg":"共產黨滾出香港"},{"pid":"3895009535240fa02c2df6d509302bcd7008ab08","tid":1354241,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:05:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">共產黨滾出香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"1756c97973718399685eb7137219c6ba3750db80","tid":1354241,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T06:06:39.000Z","ms